    "rationale": "Thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves gradation 2 against a required gradation 3; this gap is accepted because testing was conducted at two independent laboratories under a standardised protocol, and the single loading-rate condition is conservative with respect to clinical use. Overall credibility profile supports a Medium assurance level conclusion consistent with the Medium model influence and Medium decision consequence of the COU.",
